data.description: This charming 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom residence is nestled on an oversized lot, offering a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Step inside and be greeted by the warmth of original hardwood floors and the timeless allure of white window shutters, creating an ambiance that is both inviting and elegant. Experience the epitome of comfort with an efficient AC system that ensures a cozy atmosphere all year round. The property boasts impeccable landscaping, providing a picturesque backdrop for the stunning patio deck - an ideal setting for creating lasting memories during gatherings with family and friends. A striking feature of this home is the intricate wood ceiling beams that add a touch of rustic charm, harmonizing perfectly with the modern amenities. The spacious living area offers an abundance of natural light, creating an airy and welcoming space for relaxation and entertainment. Convenience is at your doorstep with the property's proximity to shopping centers, making everyday errands a breeze. With just a short 15-minute drive to the beach, indulge in the luxury of coastal living and embrace the calming allure of the ocean. Additionally, the easy access to nearby freeways caters to the needs of commuters, ensuring a seamless and efficient daily routine. Don't miss this opportunity to make this delightful property your new sanctuary. ** THIS HOME DOES NOT HAVE AN HOA **
